snippet.title: Interior Worlds - A Liminal Space Photography Game - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Interior Worlds; an ambient first person exploration game, where you'll dive into strange, yet familiar spaces.

▼▼▼ Buy the game here ▼▼▼
https://sodaraptor.itch.io/interior-worlds

Created in under 2 months by a pair of passionate game developers, Interior Worlds will have you tasked with photographing the world around you. From a roadside hotel to a dying mall and everything in between, you'll experience unsettling feelings across seven locations.

Trailer music by PSOVOD:
https://freesound.org/people/PSOVOD/sounds/415186/
